2;s:146:"Obviously, the main differences between edens garden vs doterra oils are their source buying practices and the overall cost of the final products.";i:13;s:36:"You can read our cookie policy here.";i:14;s:278:"For instance doterra only has 1 echinacea while young living has 5, doterra only has 1 frankincense young living has 2 (btw w both echinacea and frankincense they come from different plants.) young living says right with any product the ingredients they are using before buying.";i:15;s:49:"There is sooo much to learn about essential oils.";i:16;s:42:"Eden garden oils compared to young living;";i:17;s:348:"The trademarks young living®, r.c.®, raven®, digize®, dragon time®, abundance®, theives®, joy®, panaway®, gentle baby®, white angelica®, purification®, stress away®, valor®, peace and calming®, as well as the goods affiliated with these trademarks, are the property of young living oils, llc and are not in any way related to revive.";i:18;s:113:"Unlike young living or doterra, edens garden does not use distributors as a middleman for selling their products.";i:19;s:152:"If young living and doterra sold the absolute best essential oils on the market, maybe the opinion expressed in the previous section would be different.";i:20;s:78:"Young living and doterra essential oils aren’t better than all other brands.";i:21;s:180:"Their oils are touted as better than the ones you can get from eden’s garden or plant therapy, but they aren’t, there is no standard for essential oils to be considered better.";i:22;s:32:"They do this in their own farms.";i:23;s:73:"Edens garden is doing fine as well with their simple and direct approach.";i:24;s:37:"Edens garden vs doterra young living;";i:25;s:91:"All our essential oils are 100% pure, free of any fillers, synthetics or harmful chemicals.";i:26;s:95:"If you found this article helpful we would love to hear about it in the comments section below.";i:27;s:54:"And all are gc/ms tested to ensure quality and safety.";i:28;s:41:"Your email address will not be published.";i:29;s:74:"If your appetite is whetted like mine is, you’ll want to grab this book.";i:30;s:64:"The plant therapy website uses cookies for a variety of reasons.";i:31;s:94:"Their oils are all thoroughly tested in batches before they are put into edens garden bottles.";i:32;s:42:"Maybe i would feel compelled to sell them.";i:33;s:55:"I don t trust that his oils are therapeutic grade oils.";i:34;s:32:"Be first to leave comment below.";i:35;s:108:"The only other place i’ve ever seen selling edens garden oils aside from their own website was amazon.com.";i:36;s:50:"If you like doterra's oils, you are going to love.";i:37;s:36:"Doterra vs young living equivalents.";i:38;s:45:"Edens garden blends compared to young living;";i:39;s:96:"Here is a brief comparison between edens garden, young living, dōterra and mountain rose herbs.";i:40;s:69:"The results of these tests can be found on each oil’s product page.";i:41;s:80:"By accessing or using the plant therapy website you agree to the use of cookies.";i:42;s:291:"Excellent doterra vs edens garden essential oils overview posted july 26, 2017 july 26, 2017 lance this doterra vs edens garden essential oils overview explains the main similarities and differences between the companies and helps you frame up how to think about service, quality, and price.";i:43;s:54:"And all are gc/ms tested to ensure quality and safety.";i:44;s:67:"Do terra is headed by a gentlemen who worked for young living oils.";i:45;s:91:"All our essential oils are 100% pure, free of any fillers, synthetics or harmful chemicals.";i:46;s:66:"There other brands that compete with edens gardens essential oils.";i:47;s:194:"I recently got into essential oils and my boss does the whole sales thing for doterra and she swears it’s the better brand because it’s more pure and says shit on the bottle label blah blah.";i:48;s:21:"Let me just tell you.";i:49;s:45:"The company follows their standard e.d.e.n.s.";i:50;s:37:"Edens garden vs young living doterra;";i:51;s:36:"Rocky mountain oils vs young living;";i:52;s:107:"We’re doing an edens garden vs young living comparison so you can decide for yourself which brand to use.";i:53;s:41:"Your email address will not be published.";i:54;s:62:"In this post i have compared 4 different essential oil brands:";i:55;s:201:"Young living vs doterra is a question a lot of people ask when choosing an essential oil company.below is my experience with both and what i found to be the difference between young living and doterra.";i:56;s:32:"Be first to leave comment below.";i:57;s:95:"It has been quite a few years since i first investigated the different essential oil companies.";i:58;s:48:"Why is doterra more expensive than edens garden?";i:59;s:186:"Since the very first time i got an essential oil (lavender was my first) i have wondered why it had this odd edge to the fragrance that kept it from being entirely pleasant to the smell.";i:60;s:48:"Doterra vs edens garden essential oils / blends.";i:61;s:168:"Essential oil chart essential oil uses natural essential oils young living oils young living essential oils tips & tricks doterra essential oils doterra blends yl oils.";i:62;s:42:"Required fields are marked * post comment.";i:63;s:59:"There are other advantages too w young living over doterra.";i:64;s:138:"Young living oils have a pretty high standard since they control their product from the botanical seed all the way to distilling the oils.";i:65;s:70:"I’m not saying they’re necessarily worse than other essential oil.";i:66;s:116:"In the case, young living alleged that doterra founders violated their employment contracts and stole trade secrets.";i:67;s:106:"By cutting out the middleman, they have control over their direct sales and can therefore keep prices low.";i:68;s:55:"The founders wanted the oils to be pure and economical.";i:69;s:108:"If you have a favorite young living or doterra blend, learn which plant therapy oils would be right for you!";i:70;s:27:"Hi all, just a quick thing.";i:71;s:66:"This stands for effective, dedicated, educated, natural, and safe.";i:72;s:177:"The buying practices can often be a source of contention with essential oil fans, but the 3rd party testing should help put any worries to rest pertaining to purity and quality.";i:73;s:35:"Only you know what is best for you.";i:74;s:107:"Hopefully it can offer you some assistance if you are looking for a similar blend from a different company.";i:75;s:34:"Edens garden doterra young living;";i:76;s:162:"Young living, like doterra, is an mlm, you may have easier access, but most of their reps never ever ever break even and generally hemorrhage themselves of money.";i:77;s:92:"I’m glad you asked why i’m throwing out some of the best essential oil brands available.";}}